title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: The labels returned before extraction are null, while the ones after extraction are recognizable strings.
EB: The getcolumnlabel function should return the same labels before extraction as it does after extraction, in order to display recognizable strings to the end user.
SR: To reproduce, call the getcolumnlabel function on the meta data object before and after extraction and compare the results.
